            { "language": "en", "text": "Due to market conditions, the offer validity is only thirty days." },
            { "language": "fa", "text": "به‌دلیل شرایط بازار، اعتبار پیشنهاد فقط سی روز است." }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "word": "Kündigungsfrist",
